## 7. Test Resources

### Team Members:
- **Test Automation Engineer:** 1

### Required Infrastructure:
- Test Execution Machine
- Git Repository
- CI/CD Pipeline (GitHub Actions)
- Test Reporting Dashboard

## 8. Entry Criteria
- Test Plan document is approved
- Test cases are documented and reviewed
- Test environment is accessible
- Test data is prepared and available
- UI + API automation framework is set up
- All team members are trained

## 9. Exit Criteria
- All planned test cases are executed
- Test execution report is generated
- Critical and high-priority bugs are resolved
- Test coverage is ≥ 90%
- Test Automation Engineer
- Test artifacts are archived

## 10. Test Deliverables
1. Test Plan Document
2. Test Cases Specification
3. Test Automation Scripts
4. Test Execution Report
5. Defect Report
6. Test Coverage Report
7. Lessons Learned Document
8. API Test Cases Specification

## 11. Risk Analysis

### Identified Risks:

| Risk                           | Probability | Impact |               Mitigation                         |
|--------------------------------|-------------|--------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Test environment downtime      | Medium      | High   | Have backup environment; Regular health checks   |
| Test data corruption           | Low         | High   | Version control for test data; Regular backups   |
| Framework compatibility issues | Medium      | Medium | Regular framework updates; Cross-browser testing |
| Resource unavailability        | Low         | Medium | Cross-training team members; Documentation       |
| Third-party API failures       | Medium      | Medium | Use mock data; Have fallback scenarios           |

## 12. Assumptions & Dependencies
- Application is accessible and stable
- Payment gateway is in test/sandbox mode
- Public API endpoints remain available as documented
- Test data will be available throughout testing period
- Required user access and credentials will be provided
- No major application changes during test execution
- Internet connectivity is stable

